abstract: >
  MIESC is an open-source framework that brings enterprise-grade smart contract
  security analysis to every developer. It orchestrates 13 external security tools
  and 22 internal analysis modules across 9 defense layers. The latest
  full-corpus reproducible SmartBugs profile reaches 95.8% recall on 143
  contracts; adding a local 32B model raises that recall to 97.9%. A
  reproducible four-provider EVMBench local-extraction ensemble reaches 111/120
  detections (92.5% recall). MIESC runs locally by default, maps
  findings to 12 international security standards, and is freely available to
  help secure Web3 for everyone.
